        "parts": [
          {
            "text": "For dry, dehydrated skin in Katy, TX, here are some of the best facial options and spas to consider:\n\n**Facial Treatments for Hydration:**\n\n*   **HydroPeptide Moisture Infusion Ultra-Hydrating Facial:** This facial uses a blend of triple-weight hyaluronic acid to deeply hydrate multiple layers of the skin, strengthen the skin barrier, and improve radiance. It enhances moisture retention and balance. Restore Hyper Wellness in Katy, TX offers this service.\n*   **HydraFacial:** This non-invasive treatment cleanses, exfoliates, extracts impurities, and hydrates the skin. It infuses hydrating serums with antioxidants, peptides, and hyaluronic acid. Ageless MedSpa Katy offers HydraFacial treatments.\n*   **Custom Facial:** Many spas offer custom facials tailored to your skin's specific needs. These facials can be designed to address dryness and dehydration by infusing moisture and restoring the skin's balance. SkinSpirit Katy and Anita's Skin Care Clinic are among the places that offer custom facials.\n*   **Signature Classic Refresh Facial:** This facial is designed to hydrate, soften, and smooth the skin. It includes a cleanse, exfoliation with Mandelic acid and Mangosteen extracts, and the use of Goji Berry antioxidants, hyaluronic acid, and natural plant extracts. Spavia Cinco Ranch offers this facial.\n*   **Age Defense Facial:** This facial hydrates, brightens, and tightens the skin with Vitamin C and hyaluronic acid to nourish and plump the skin. It is available at Spavia Cinco Ranch.\n*   **Brightening Blossom Facial:** This facial targets dryness and fine lines while gently exfoliating the skin. Spavia Cinco Ranch offers this service for spring renewal.\n\n**Spas and Med Spas in Katy, TX:**\n\n*   **Restore Hyper Wellness:** Offers the HydroPeptide Moisture Infusion Ultra-Hydrating Facial.\n    *   Address: 23116 Cinco Ranch Boulevard, Katy, TX 77494\n*   **Face to Face Spa:** This beauty med spa offers classic facials and Hydrafacials. They focus on understanding your goals to personalize your experience.\n*   **Spavia Cinco Ranch:** Provides result-driven skincare with a variety of choices, including clean clinical active ingredients, natural skincare ingredients, organic ingredients, and vegan skincare.\n*   **SkinSpirit:** Offers custom facials tailored to your skin's needs.\n    *   Phone: (281) 769-8644\n*   **Ageless MedSpa Katy:** Offers HydraFacial treatments.\n*   **Katy Med Tech Spa:** Offers personalized treatments and Ageless Signature Facials.\n*    **Anita's Skin Care Clinic:** Specializes in holistic skincare and customizes treatments to address unique skin concerns.\n*   **Luminous MediSpa Katy:** Offers a wide range of services, including RF micro-needling and hydro facials.\n*   **LUXE Medical Aesthetics:** Offers facials that deliver results, customizing every treatment to meet your unique needs.\n    *   Address: 21770 Kingsland Blvd., Katy, TX 77450\n    *   Phone: 833.998.LUXE (5893)\n*   **The Only Facial:** Specializes in one signature facial customized to individual skin types and concerns.\n\nWhen booking, consider asking for a consultation to discuss your specific skin concerns and determine the best facial for your needs.\n"
          }
        ],
        "role": "model"
      },
